IPO shares (shares)                      : 507,600,000
IPO price (baht)                         : 24.00
Business description                     :
The company manufactures and distributes paint and coating products for end user
 and contractors.
The main products are classified into 2 main categories.

1. Decorative Paint and Coating Products

2. Non-Decorative Paint and Coating Products such as wood coating products, 
construction chemical products, heavy duty coating products and hardware
Remark                                   :
The number of shares offered to the public is 507.6 million shares allocated 
into
1) New shares of 254 million shares
2) Existing shares of 253.6 million shares

IPO Subscription Period : 27-29 September 2017 and 2-4 October 2017 (Please see 
the information memorandum of TOA through PDF file.)
